## Your RBAC Schema (What You Actually Have)

From your schema documentation:

```
dpah_modules          → top level (RMS, HRMS, MRR, ANALYTICS...)
dpah_collections      → belongs to a module via module_id
dpah_agents           → belongs to a collection via collection_id
dpah_roles            → JUNIOR, MID, SENIOR
dpah_user_roles       → emp_id → role_id mapping
dpah_module_usergroups → module_id → group_idx mapping
dpah_role_agent_access → role_id + group_id + agent_id (three-way mapping)
```

The permission resolution is: **who is this user → what role do they have → what group are they in → what agents can that role+group access → which collection does each agent belong to → which module is that collection in**

